OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,FBritish lives are "in danger" after
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer gave the US
OL,8,Fpermission to strike Iranian missile
OL,9,Fsites targeting the Strait of Hormuz
OL,10,Ffrom UK bases, Tehran has warned.
OL,12,FMinisters agreed to the move on Friday
OL,13,Fafternoon having previously limited
OL,14,Fthe US to only using the bases to hit
OL,15,Fmissile sites targeting British
OL,16,Finterests in the region.
OL,18,FUS President Donald Trump said the UK
OL,19,F"should have acted a lot faster" in
OL,20,Fgiving the US permission.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@]O]{D@AOU{D@`O]
