OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774078637
OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,FHe has already piled pressure on Nato
OL,7,Fallies, calling them "cowards" for
OL,8,Frefusing to offer warships to reopen
OL,9,Fthe Strait.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer had previously
OL,12,Fgranted the US permission only for
OL,13,F"defensive" action against Iranian
OL,14,Fmissile sites from RAF Fairford in
OL,15,FGloucestershire and Diego Garcia in
OL,16,Fthe Indian Ocean.
OL,18,FHe will hold a Cobra meeting next week
OL,19,Fto discuss plans to help households
OL,20,Fwith the cost of living caused by the
OL,21,Fwar, it is understood.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@^O]uD@AOUuD@KO]
