OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters outside the
OL,7,FWhite House, Mr Trump said: "It's been
OL,8,Fa very late response from the UK.
OL,10,F"I'm surprised because the
OL,11,Frelationship is so good, but this has
OL,12,Fnever happened before.
OL,14,F"They were really pretty much our
OL,15,Ffirst ally, all over the world."
OL,17,FReferring to Diego Garcia, he said:
OL,18,F"They didn't want us to use the
OL,19,Fisland, the so-called island, which
OL,20,Ffor some reason they gave up rights to
OL,21,Fit.
OL,26,@oD@]OUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@`O]zD@AOU
