OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,F"I was a little surprised in the UK,
OL,7,Fto be honest. They should have acted a
OL,8,Flot faster."
OL,10,FIranian foreign minister Abbas
OL,11,FAraghchi said "Iran will exercise its
OL,12,Fright to self-defence".
OL,14,FPosting on X, he said: "Vast majority
OL,15,Fof the British People do not want any
OL,16,Fpart in the Israel-US war of choice on
OL,17,FIran.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]sD@OOUtD@VO]vD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
