CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774078637
OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,F"Ignoring his own People, Mr Starmer
OL,7,Fis putting British lives in danger by
OL,8,Fallowing UK bases to be used for
OL,9,Faggression against Iran. Iran will
OL,10,Fexercise its right to self-defence."
OL,12,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,13,Fdescribed the Sir Keir's move as the
OL,14,F"mother of all U-turns" in a post on X.
OL,16,FThe Liberal Democrats and the Green
OL,17,FParty said granting further permission
OL,18,Ffor the US to use British bases must
OL,19,Ffirst have a parliamentary vote.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]vD@AOUvD@WO]
