OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,FDefence sources have stressed the
OL,7,Fsituation was so dangerous that not
OL,8,Fmany nations would be willing to put
OL,9,Fwarships "in the middle of that threat
OL,10,Fright now".
OL,12,FPosting on his Truth Social platform
OL,13,Fon Friday evening, Mr Trump said the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz "will have to be
OL,15,Fguarded and policed" by "other Nations
OL,16,Fwho use it ` The United States does
OL,17,Fnot!"
OL,26,@qD@JOUrD@JO]vD@ROUwD@TO]wD@YOUyD@EO]
