OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774078637
OL,3,CBritish lives 'in danger' after UK
OL,4,Cbacks US strikes on Iran from its bases
OL,6,F"If asked, we will help these
OL,7,Fcountries in their Hormuz efforts, but
OL,8,Fit shouldn't be necessary once Iran's
OL,9,Fthreat is eradicated," he said,
OL,10,Fadding: "Importantly, it will be an
OL,11,Feasy Military Operation for them.
OL,13,F"We are getting very close to meeting
OL,14,Four objectives as we consider winding
OL,15,Fdown our great Military efforts in the
OL,16,FMiddle East with respect to the
OL,17,FTerrorist Regime of Iran."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]rD@IOUuD@AOUyD@ZO]
